schools.name: Village Academy On The Art & Sara Jo Kobacker Campus

data.description:
Over half acre PRIVATE lot with serene golf course VIEWS & lush tropical gardens! Located on a quiet CUL DE SAC, this spacious home is architecturally appealing with a grand circular 300 ft driveway. There is nothing like this - a bright,  private oasis! Three large split bedrooms, plus a study (can be 4th br), pool bath & massive screened patio around the heated salt water pool. Indoor/outdoor wet bar makes for perfect entertaining! This well-maintained home boasts a newer roof, screened lanai, vaulted ceilings, two laundries, two primary baths, many large closets, summer kitchen with new Weber grill, steam showers, mix of impact & electric shutters. The exclusive Bocaire Country Club is a boutique mandatory membership Country Club  with only 239 homes on one circle ...no divided sections. It is an inclusive, friendly and active community, welcoming all! Parents, children and grandchildren included in the membership. Renowned championship golf course, competitive and social golf, tennis & pickle ball programs, resort-like aquatics center, 24 hour fitness center with diverse fitness classes, high-end dining and many fun social events and programs. The Bocaire Master Plan is under way - the clubhouse is under construction to be completed this season with a new casual dining area, remodeled dining rooms, card rooms, new enlarged kitchen, indoor/outdoor bar and extended patio. Additional tennis court and pickle ball courts are being built, a new modernized front entrance and new Golf Course maintenance buildings will be erected. Very exciting times at Bocaire! 
One of the most eastern country clubs in Boca Raton, Bocaire is in an A school district with many desirable public and private schools. Close to beaches, restaurants, entertainment and to both Atlantic Avenue in Delray Beach and Mizner Park Boca Raton.
